https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/3GbMlGMPn8H7AwinlL0vguECrt.jpg Bettie Page was America's number one pin-up girl in the 1950s and became a cult icon. This biopic tells the story of the last 3 years of her short-lived career, recreating the incriminating bondage films which gave her the nickname "Dark Angel", and led to her mysterious disappearance.
